Nigerian singer, David Adeleke, popularly known as Davido, has revealed that his billionaire father, Adedeji Adeleke surprised him with another land in Banana Island, Lekki, Lagos. The ‘Omo Baba Olowo’ crooner disclosed this on Sunday in a tweet via his official Twitter page, while expressing his love for his father. He wrote, “Woke up to another Land from popsi in banana again ! Such a dope father ! Love u pops.” Osun 2022: There’s Politics In My Blood, Davido Declares Davido Writes About His Trust In God Recall that Davido’s father is a business magnate, president of Adeleke University and also the CEO of Pacific Holdings Limited.